      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AYDEN'S WARRIOR (1) is in sizzling form lately, rocketing around Sandown in 41.59 to score two back then following on with a 41.60 win over 715m at Sandown. Should be in this for a long way. TEXAS PRESIDENT (4) boasts a strong record this journey with six wins and nine minors from 18 tries. Was out of placings last time (34.63) at Sandown in a Grade 4/5, finishing sixth and beaten 5 lengths. Among the main chances. URANA PARALLAX (8) filled the minor money three on end before breaking through for a deserved win last time, scoring at The Meadows over 730m (42.93). Winner at his latest appearance in the quickest time on the card. Makes plenty of appeal if runs up to latest. SCOTCH TIME (2) is worth including after a top-three finish most recently.",
